<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>As different logging styles are appropriate for varied situations, Zend_Log should be able to support logging:</p>

<h1>the log level value (e.g., "16")</h1>

<h1>the log level name or string (e.g., "SEVERE")</h1>

<h1>both the log level name and value, in whatever order (e.g., "16 SEVERE")</h1>

<p>This currently affects the "format" option of the adapter classes.</p>

